OL,3,C'Fancy a two-thirds'? Study suggest
OL,4,Cshrinking pints to boost nation's
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FResearchers found the amount of beer
OL,8,Fsold by the venues taking part had
OL,9,Ffallen by 10%, as ITV News' Kelly
OL,10,FForan reports
OL,12,FWords by Olivia Mustafa, ITV News
OL,13,FProducer
OL,15,FHow would you feel if you ordered and
OL,16,Fpint - and it turned out to be two
OL,17,Fthirds smaller than you were expecting?
OL,19,FA study has suggested shrinking the
OL,20,Fmuch-loved British pint could improve
OL,21,Fthe health of the nation.
