OL,3,C'Fancy a two-thirds'? Study suggest
OL,4,Cshrinking pints to boost nation's
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FThe trial saw a dozen pubs, bars and
OL,8,Frestaurants swap their regular pint
OL,9,Fglasses with a smaller measure, just
OL,10,Ftwo thirds of the original size.
OL,12,FBy the end of the study, researchers
OL,13,Ffound the amount of beer sold by the
OL,14,Fvenues taking part had fallen by 10%.
OL,16,FThe team believe a drop in beer sales
OL,17,Fcould lessen the impact of alcohol-
OL,18,Frelated harm, which claims thousands
OL,19,Fof lives in Britain each year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
