OL,3,C'Fancy a two-thirds'? Study suggest
OL,4,Cshrinking pints to boost nation's
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,F"It's hard to imagine people saying,
OL,8,F'would you like to come for a two-
OL,9,Fthirds?', instead of 'would you like
OL,10,Fto come for a pint?'," said Professor
OL,11,FDame Theresa Marteau, study leader and
OL,12,Fdirector of the behaviour and health
OL,13,Fresearch unit at the University of
OL,14,FCambridge.
OL,16,F"But increasingly, different beers are
OL,17,Fsold in different sizes and it may
OL,18,Fjust be one of those things that the
OL,19,FBritish population can get used to."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
