OL,7,FProfessor Dame Theresa Marteau
OL,8,Fbelieves the tactic could "definitely"
OL,9,Fcontribute to the health of the
OL,10,Fpopulation.
OL,12,FThe research says reducing the amount
OL,13,Fof alcohol we drink is a global public
OL,14,Fhealth priority. According to a 2022
OL,15,Fstudy, drinking even within the NHS
OL,16,Fguidelines of 14 units of alcohol a
OL,17,Fweek for women can still increase the
OL,18,Frisk of heart disease and stroke.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
