OL,3,C'Fancy a two-thirds'? Study suggest
OL,4,Cshrinking pints to boost nation's
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FThe team were looking into whether
OL,8,Fpeople would be tempted to order more
OL,9,Fbeer to compensate for smaller glass
OL,10,Fsize - but found the measure resulted
OL,11,Fin people drinking less.
OL,13,FThe study invited around 1,700 venues
OL,14,Fto take part - but in the end, only 13
OL,15,Fagreed. They were offered compensation
OL,16,Fto account for any drop in income from
OL,17,Fselling smaller pints.
