OL,7,FProfessor Dame Marteau said that was
OL,8,Fmore than they were expecting, as none
OL,9,Fvolunteered to join the study when it
OL,10,Fwas first attempted in 2019.
OL,12,FInstead, the 2019 study offered the
OL,13,Ftwo thirds-size glass as an option,
OL,14,Falongside the regular pint. Unlike
OL,15,Fthis year's study, this was not found
OL,16,Fto reduce the amount of beer consumed.
