OL,7,FShe acknowledged there may well be a
OL,8,Fmeasure of resistance from pub
OL,9,Flandlords and venue owners, who would
OL,10,Fhave little incentive to start serving
OL,11,Fsmaller pints.
OL,13,F"The earnings dropped by around 5%. At
OL,14,Fthe end of the study, all the
OL,15,Fparticipating pubs had reintroduced
OL,16,Fthe pint serving size and none of them
OL,17,Fchose to remove it again," Professor
OL,18,FDame Marteau said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
