OL,7,F"Unless this becomes part of licensing
OL,8,Fregulation, this isn't something pubs
OL,9,Fand bars are going to adopt on their
OL,10,Fown."
OL,12,FThe study appears to support a wealth
OL,13,Fof other research, Professor Dame
OL,14,FMarteau said, into how portion sizes
OL,15,Fcan affect how we eat and drink.
OL,17,F"The smaller the portion, the less you
OL,18,Fwill consume," she said.
